CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

October 7, 2008

[Cite as 10/07/2008 Case Announcements #2, 2008-0hio-5216.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-1832. Roe v. Planned Parenthood Southwest Ohio Region.

Hamilton App. No. C-060557, 173 Ohio App.3d 414, 2007-0hio-4318. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellees’ emergency motion to seal exhibit A to appellants’ memo opposing expedited motion to prohibit use of proposed exhibit at oral argument,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
